    "ideation": "The 'Peeking Eye' emoji represents a mix of terror and insatiable curiosity. The animation must capture the push-pull of wanting to hide while being unable to look away. The face begins in a full-hide state—eyes clamped shut and mouth tight. Then, the animation enters a jerky, nervous sequence where the right eye 'peeks' by opening slightly while the left remains tightly closed. The asymmetry is key: the robot is literally cheating its own fear. The mouth acts as a nervous indicator, moving from a tight line to a fast-shimmering, uncertain wave as the robot sees something it probably shouldn't. Color shifts from a fearful, bruised indigo to a startled, high-contrast yellow-orange as the 'peek' lands on its target.",
